snippet: Indonesia said Monday that it had rescued 120 Afghan migrants from a leaking wooden ship headed to Australia.
abstract: Indonesian officials announce that they have rescued 120 Afghan migrants from a leaking wooden ship headed to Australia.
lead_paragraph: Indonesia said Monday that it had rescued 120 Afghan migrants from a leaking wooden ship headed to Australia.
